overview:
Integrated in the year 1977, at Delhi (India), we, “Sona Music Palace”, are renowned as one of the leading manufacturers, trader and supplier of superior quality array of Drum Sets, Guitar, Dholak, Harmonium, Tabla and Keyboards, etc. This series of products comprises Premier Drum Sets, GB & A Drum Sets, D.B Drum Sets, Pluto Guitars, Cort Guitars, Fender Guitars, Grenada Guitars, Professional Dholak, Scale Changers Harmoniums, Copper Pair Tabla, Roland Keyboards, etc.

Infrastructure: The achievement that we have gained in this domain is due to the fact that since our inauguration, we have paid full attention towards constructing a sophisticated infrastructural facility. The machines installed at our unit empower us to design and develop the best quality Wash Burn Guitars, Ibanez Acoustics, etc. that have lustrous shine with other unmatched attributes.

Processes: Since the integration of our organization, we are serving our highly reputed clients with the superior quality musical items that help us in building long-term relation with them. Being a quality conscious company, we always prefer to provide clients high quality range of Wash Burn Guitars, Ibanez Acoustics, etc. as per the set universal norms.

Team / Manpower: We have recruited a skilled team of professionals, who help us in offering premium quality assortment of Wash Burn Guitars, Ibanez Acoustics, etc. Our experienced professionals strive hard to know the diverse demands of our prestigious clients and provide all the offered products accordingly.

Our Products: Premier Drum Sets, GB & A Drum Sets, D.B Drum Sets, Pluto Guitars, Cort Guitars, Fender Guitars, Grenada Guitars, Professional Dholak, Scale Changers Harmoniums, Copper Pair Tabla, Roland Keyboards, etc.
